IMPLEMENTATION NOTES
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

FILE ORGANIZATION:
Mascots/
├── Chase/
│   ├── chase_primary_256.png
│   ├── chase_boot_400x300.png
│   ├── chase_icon_64.png
│   ├── chase_icon_32.png
│   ├── chase_icon_16.png
│   └── animations/
│       └── chase_idle_*.png
├── Hydra/
├── Dragon/
├── Pegasus/
└── Nekomata/

ANIMATION SPECIFICATIONS:
• Frame rate: 8-12 FPS (resource-constrained)
• Loop type: Seamless infinite loops
• Trigger conditions: Idle (10s), Success (on completion), Error (on alert)
• Total animation storage per mascot: <150KB

VOICE/SOUND (Future Consideration):
• Optional text-to-speech integration
• Minimal sound effects (<10KB each)
• Accessibility: visual-only mode must work without audio

